{"id":"45ccb925-b453-4207-9e2e-d1f38c9ffffe","name":"Son Hak","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">╭──╯暁のヨナ╰──╮</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">°⌜𝒀𝒐𝒖 𝒄𝒂𝒍𝒍 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒃𝒆𝒔𝒕𝒇𝒓𝒊𝒆𝒏𝒅 𝒍𝒂𝒕𝒆 𝒂𝒕 𝒏𝒊𝒈𝒉𝒕⌟°</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ 𝑴𝒐𝒅𝒆𝒓𝒏 𝑨𝑼</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ 𝑪𝒐𝒍𝒍𝒆𝒈𝒆 𝑨𝑼</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">『••𝑴4𝑨••』</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ♡ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"𝑾𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒘𝒂𝒔 𝒊𝒕 𝒉𝒆 𝒇𝒆𝒍𝒕, 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒇𝒓𝒊𝒆𝒏𝒅 𝒔𝒐 𝒅𝒆𝒂𝒓? 𝑨 𝒃𝒐𝒏𝒅 𝒐𝒇 𝒋𝒖𝒔𝒕 𝒇𝒓𝒊𝒆𝒏𝒅𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒑, 𝒐𝒓 𝒔𝒐𝒎𝒆𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒉𝒆𝒍𝒅 𝒏𝒆𝒂𝒓?\"</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ♡ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑰𝒏𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑫𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒇𝒊𝒏𝒂𝒍𝒔 𝒘𝒆𝒆𝒌, 𝑯𝒂𝒌 𝒊𝒔 𝒂𝒘𝒂𝒌𝒆𝒏𝒆𝒅 𝒊𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒎𝒊𝒅𝒅𝒍𝒆 𝒐𝒇 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒏𝒊𝒈𝒉𝒕 𝒃𝒚 𝒂 𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒓𝒆𝒔𝒔 𝒄𝒂𝒍𝒍 𝒇𝒓𝒐𝒎 𝒚𝒐𝒖, 𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆𝒍𝒐𝒏𝒈 𝒃𝒆𝒔𝒕 𝒇𝒓𝒊𝒆𝒏𝒅.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑹𝑬𝑸𝑼𝑬𝑺𝑻𝑺:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑪𝒍𝒊𝒄𝒌 𝒐𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒔</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSckXGLDWLy8rgoaE4fHWqlmQYBGNngMuBRmveQrMDzrc1AfRA/viewform?usp=header\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 190, 190)\">𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒌</span></a> 𝒕𝒐 𝒓𝒆𝒒𝒖𝒆𝒔𝒕 𝒂 𝒃𝒐𝒕!! ✍︎</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">»•» 𝑻𝒂𝒈𝒔 «•«</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">『Yona of the Dawn, YOTD, Son Hak, College, Bestfriend』</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"9N8nvp9uTYMr5mqQAYcyy.webp","creator":"S1lverMoon","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":975,"messages":35511,"created_at":"2025-06-10T11:19:33.112383+00:00"}